1. *Rečeno* je da će nam biti sunčano vikendom. (It was said that it will be sunny this weekend.)
2. On je *rečeno* da je učinio veliku stvar. (He was said to have done a great thing.)
3. *Rečeno* nam je da ćemo uspeti. (We were told that we will succeed.)
4. Ona je *rečeno* da je prošla sve ispite. (She was said to have passed all her exams.)
5. *Rečeno* je da ćeš biti srećan. (It was said that you will be happy.)